Pod-BBCode 1.5

Simple module converts .pod files into BBCode syntax, for the ease of
posting POD documents to vBulletin (or other system which use BBCode)
forums.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install


